testsuite.name: Script.SendToExport
testsuite.system-out: Scenario 01: Log into EWA Enter valid user name into username field Enter valid password into password field Select a Room Click Login button Session for user is already active.Do you want to create new session? dialog box displayed User click on OK button, User logged in successfully...

Step Details: Exporting blank document list Click on My account tab. Logout, What's New, HelpExport, Offline documents, DocuSign documents,Download Outlook drag and dropChange password options are available Click on Export button. DocumentList(Current Date)_(DocumentID).csv file will get downloaded Click on the downloaded .csv file An excel file with following headings will open:Document name, Type, Pages, Created on, Last modified. If there is no data then it will display as ' No data available in table'

Step Details: Exporting document list Navigate a tree till folder level Lists the documents present in that folder Go to My accounts Tab Export button is enabled Click on Export Button DocumentList(Current Date)_(DocumentID).csv file will get downloaded An excel file with following headings will open Document name, Type, Pages, Created on, Last modified, Comments, References

Step Details: Exporting blank search list Click on Search tab and search any value. Click on My accounts tab. Export button is enabled Click on Export button. SearchList(CurentDate)_(DocumentID).csv file will get downloaded. A Downloaded excel file has following headings:Document name, Type, Pages, Created on, Last modified. As there is no values, it will display as 'No data available in table'

Step Details: Verify Export Expand the cabinet Expand the drawer Click on the folder Open a document AlertISNotPresent Scenario 05:Verify Export with convert to PDF Open a document and select a page Click on sendto tool icon Select export submenu Select convert to pdf radio button Select the burn annotation check box User click on export dialog OK button The document exported succcessfully

Scenario 04:verifying export functionality retain format,with average quality and zip password Open a document and select a page Click on sendto tool icon Select export submenu Select retain radio button Click on export dialog OK button Document exported successfull
